message.distributionDefaultInviterIdTip.message: Default inviter's user ID, if the distribution link does not carry the inviter_id parameter, the user ID will be used as the inviter by default.

message.distributionForceInviterIdTip.message: Forced inviter's user ID, if this ID is set, regardless of whether the distribution link carries the inviter_id parameter, the user ID will be forced as the inviter.

message.originTip.message: Site domain, site configuration is bound to the domain, and the site domain cannot be changed.

message.titleTip.message: Site title, displayed in the browser tab.

message.descriptionTip.message: Site description, located in the site's meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.logoTip.message: Site logo, displayed at the top of the site menu when the menu is expanded.

message.faviconTip.message: Site favicon, displayed in the browser tab.

message.adminsTip.message: Site admin ID, by default, the user who first creates the site will become the admin. Only site admins can manage the site.

message.adminsTip2.message: Admin IDs can be added or removed here, user IDs can be viewed at https://auth.acedata.cloud

message.keywordsTip.message: Site keywords, located in the site's meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.keywordsTip2.message: Site keywords can be added or removed here. The more precise the keywords, the better for SEO optimization.
